01:45:01.210 --> 01:45:03.210
Part of this complete breakfast.

01:45:03.210 --> 01:45:04.210
Yeah, they're very good.

01:45:04.210 --> 01:45:07.210
And they're going to be very big news.

01:45:08.210 --> 01:45:10.210
Now, the sneaking begins again.

01:45:10.210 --> 01:45:15.860
With Are You Afraid of the Dark?

01:45:15.860 --> 01:45:16.860
Somebody help!

01:45:16.860 --> 01:45:30.700
I can hear you. I know. I've tried.

01:45:30.700 --> 01:45:31.700
Who is this?

01:45:31.700 --> 01:45:33.700
Have you forgotten already?

01:45:33.700 --> 01:45:34.700
It's Billy Baxter.

01:45:34.700 --> 01:45:37.700
Oh, man. What is this place?

01:45:37.700 --> 01:45:38.700
Why am I here?

01:45:38.700 --> 01:45:40.700
You never should have messed with the phone.

01:45:40.700 --> 01:45:41.700
Now they've got you.

01:45:41.700 --> 01:45:44.700
No, I'm going to call my parents.

01:45:44.700 --> 01:45:45.700
But on that phone you won't.

01:45:45.700 --> 01:45:47.700
It only takes incoming calls.

01:45:47.700 --> 01:45:48.700
But you called me.

01:45:48.700 --> 01:45:50.700
That's because you called me first.

01:45:50.700 --> 01:45:52.700
Maybe you'll be lucky to stay on the phone.

01:45:52.700 --> 01:45:54.700
Someone might hear you someday.

01:45:54.700 --> 01:45:56.700
Wait! Don't hang up!

01:45:56.700 --> 01:46:17.100
Yeah, yeah, hang up.

01:46:17.100 --> 01:46:23.580
Hey, Annie. They got Jake. Just like you said.

01:46:23.580 --> 01:46:25.580
It's the phone, please.

01:46:25.580 --> 01:46:27.580
We went down to the phone company.

01:46:27.580 --> 01:46:29.580
Who are you? And how do you know my name?

01:46:29.580 --> 01:46:31.580
What? It's me.

01:46:31.580 --> 01:46:33.580
Get out of here before I call the police.

01:46:33.580 --> 01:46:35.580
Hey, it's me, Chris. Jake's friend.

01:46:35.580 --> 01:46:36.580
They got him.

01:46:36.580 --> 01:46:39.580
I don't know you, and I don't know any Jake.

01:46:39.580 --> 01:46:40.580
Comacops.

01:46:40.580 --> 01:46:42.580
Wait. Jake's your brother.

01:46:42.580 --> 01:46:43.580
What is with you?

01:46:43.580 --> 01:46:46.580
Look, I don't have any brother, okay?

01:46:46.580 --> 01:46:48.580
Now get out of here.

01:46:48.580 --> 01:46:51.090
You're not kidding, are you?

01:46:51.090 --> 01:46:53.090
No, I'm not kidding. I'll be in you.

01:46:53.090 --> 01:46:55.090
Hey!

01:46:55.090 --> 01:46:57.090
I'll prove it to you.

01:46:57.090 --> 01:47:01.840
This is Jake's bed.

01:47:01.840 --> 01:47:02.840
Boom.

01:47:02.840 --> 01:47:06.090
Are you going to get out of here or do I call the cops?

01:47:06.090 --> 01:47:07.090
The cops, yeah.

01:47:07.090 --> 01:47:09.090
You told us a story about the phone police

01:47:09.090 --> 01:47:11.090
and a kid named Billy Baxter.

01:47:11.090 --> 01:47:12.090
You know the story?

01:47:12.090 --> 01:47:14.090
Yeah, I know it.

01:47:14.090 --> 01:47:17.090
Except the way I heard it, they got a kid named O'Brien.

01:47:18.090 --> 01:47:20.090
A Jake O'Brien.

01:47:20.090 --> 01:47:22.090
Jake O'Brien?

01:47:22.090 --> 01:47:51.360
Those guys look fast.

01:47:51.360 --> 01:48:06.220
Jake, take it easy. It's me.

01:48:06.220 --> 01:48:09.220
Chris, get me out of here, man. This place is nuts.

01:48:09.220 --> 01:48:12.220
I didn't do anything wrong. You've got to help me.

01:48:12.220 --> 01:48:14.220
Whoa. Calm down.

01:48:14.220 --> 01:48:16.220
Get Annie. Get my parents.

01:48:16.220 --> 01:48:18.220
I can't do that, Jake.

01:48:18.220 --> 01:48:20.220
Why not? You've got to do something

01:48:20.220 --> 01:48:22.220
or I'll be stuck in here forever.

01:48:22.220 --> 01:48:25.220
Listen, this whole thing is weirder than you even know.

01:48:26.220 --> 01:48:28.220
I'm scared, Chris.

01:48:28.220 --> 01:48:31.220
Me too, but I've got a plan.

01:48:31.220 --> 01:48:34.220
Maybe we can beat the phone police at the wrong game.

01:48:34.220 --> 01:50:02.890
Hey, kid, I told you. Answer the phone.

01:50:02.890 --> 01:53:52.150
I've got to tell you something.

01:53:52.150 --> 01:53:54.150
After you got caught, what's your house?

01:53:54.150 --> 01:54:12.980
This is Jake and your brother.

01:54:12.980 --> 01:54:14.980
You've got to remember them now.

01:54:14.980 --> 01:54:16.980
Where do you get these friends from, Jake?

01:54:16.980 --> 01:54:19.980
Do you order them from the back of comics?

01:54:19.980 --> 01:54:21.980
You remember them? You know who he is?

01:54:21.980 --> 01:54:25.980
Yeah. In fact, I'd like to forget him if they're good.

01:54:25.980 --> 01:54:34.380
Believe this.

01:54:34.380 --> 01:54:39.440
Your room's back to normal.

01:54:39.440 --> 01:54:41.440
What are you two yams talking about?

01:54:41.440 --> 01:54:45.170
You two are losing it.

01:54:45.170 --> 01:54:47.170
Annie, don't. It's the phone police.

01:54:47.170 --> 01:54:48.170
Phone police?

01:54:48.170 --> 01:54:50.170
Airhead. I made that up.

01:54:50.170 --> 01:54:52.170
But it's true. They caught me.

01:54:52.170 --> 01:54:53.170
Yeah, I wish.

01:54:53.170 --> 01:54:56.790
House pizza.

01:54:56.790 --> 01:55:00.550
One jumbo extra cheese.

01:55:00.550 --> 01:55:02.550
I'll dress to hold the anchovies.

01:55:02.550 --> 01:55:09.060
Did you guys order pizza?

01:55:09.060 --> 01:55:11.060
It's two, three, eight, not three, two, eight.

01:55:11.060 --> 01:55:19.470
I can't believe you guys bought that story with the phone police.

01:55:19.470 --> 01:55:22.470
I'm talking about the gullible.

01:55:22.470 --> 01:55:30.360
I'm going to lie down.

01:55:30.360 --> 01:55:31.360
I'm exhausted.

01:55:31.360 --> 01:55:35.090
It did happen though, didn't it?

01:55:35.090 --> 01:56:11.330
We made another prank call.

01:56:11.330 --> 01:56:15.330
Because they were never sure if the phone police were really real.

01:56:15.330 --> 01:56:17.330
Or if they could believe anything else.

01:56:17.330 --> 01:56:20.330
They ever saw again.

01:56:20.330 --> 01:56:24.180
The end.

01:56:24.180 --> 01:56:26.180
Excellent, Tucker.

01:56:26.180 --> 01:56:29.180
Great story to that story.

01:56:29.180 --> 01:56:33.180
I declare this meeting of the Midnight Society closed.

01:56:33.180 --> 01:57:44.800
In just 166 hours and counting.

01:57:44.800 --> 01:57:47.800
Oh, perhaps you're...

